  "Say": {
    "_dirName": "Say",
    "_dirType": "sub",
    "0": {
      "_dirName": "0",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Hey there! Are you enjoying the mini-games? I can make a new Omok Set if you gather a few items for me. How about it, want to give it a try?"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Good! To make a #t4080003#, I need one each of #b#t4031055#, #t4031056#, and #t4031057##k. You should be able to get them easily by defeating #o6#, #o8#, and #o9# found around #m10001000#, so please bring them to me. I'll be waiting for you right here."
        }
      },
      "no": {
        "_dirName": "no",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Hey, sometimes you just need to take a break and look around! If you change your mind, talk to me anytime."
        }
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "You've gathered everything I asked for! That couldn't have been easy—you're amazing! Alright! Time for me to show off my skills! Just wait a moment~ I'll craft your #b#t4080003##k in no time. Heave-ho!"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "You got your #b#t4080003##k, right? You can use this item anywhere in Maple World to open a mini-game room and have fun with others. If you achieve a high score, something great is sure to happen. I'll be cheering you on from here, so give it your best shot!"
        },
        "1": {
          "_dirName": "1",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Oh, right. If you ever have any questions about Omok, just ask me anytime. I plan on staying here for a while. Now then, go on and try hard to become the ultimate mini-game champion, surpassing even me! Though... that's probably not going to happen. Anyway... I'm busy, so I'll see you later~"
        }
      },
